y aware of [what is in the minds of] all beings that are in the heavens and on earth. But, indeed, We did endow some of the prophets more highly than others -just as We bestowed upon David a book of divine wisdom [in token of Our grace]","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2084.mp3","surahId":17,"words":[{"id":51564,"position":1,"arabic":"وَرَبُّكَ","translation":"এবং তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51565,"position":2,"arabic":"أَعْلَمُ","translation":"খুব জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51566,"position":3,"arabic":"بِمَن","translation":"সম্বন্ধে ঐ যা","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51567,"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে আছে","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51568,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশমন্ডলীর","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51569,"position":6,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضِ ۗ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51571,"position":7,"arabic":"وَلَقَدْ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51572,"position":8,"arabic":"فَضَّلْنَا","translation":"আমরা মর্যাদা দিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51573,"position":9,"arabic":"بَعْضَ","translation":"কাউকে","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51574,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِيِّـۧنَ","translation":"নাবীদের মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51575,"position":11,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51576,"position":12,"arabic":"بَعْضٍۢ ۖ","translation":"কারও","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":51578,"position":13,"arabic":"وَءَاتَيْنَا","translation":"এবং আমরা দিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/017_055_015.mp3","char